110
00:04:27,357 --> 00:04:28,596
- Yes.
- Homigot is amazing.

111
00:04:28,597 --> 00:04:31,026
- Happy New Year.
- Happy New Year.

112
00:04:31,027 --> 00:04:32,667
- Happy New Year.
- Happy New Year!

113
00:04:33,037 --> 00:04:34,437
Happy New Year.

114
00:04:35,037 --> 00:04:36,266
