187
00:06:47,797 --> 00:06:50,667
- Yes.
- I'm a bit flustered and confused.

188
00:06:51,237 --> 00:06:53,236
- Say thank-you.
- Say thank-you.

189
00:06:53,237 --> 00:06:54,606
Thank you for your support.

190
00:06:54,607 --> 00:06:56,077
It's been just three months.

191
00:06:56,677 --> 00:07:00,517
